Join the Conversation To find out more about Facebook commenting please read the Conversation Guidelines and FAQs Astumbo Elementary School on heightened alert, drug sweep at middle school Haidee V Eugenio, heugenio@guampdn.com Published 2:27 p.m. ChT Nov. 7, 2017 | Updated 5:23 p.m. ChT Nov. 7, 2017 A drug-detector dog sniffs through items at Astumbo Middle School Tuesday morning, after a tip given to Guam Crime Stoppers indicated possible drug activity at the Dededo campus. No contraband was found. (Photo: Photo courtesy of the Guam Department of Education) CONNECT COMMENT EMAIL MORE Astumbo Elementary School in Dededo was placed on heightened alert after a former employee of food service contractor Sodexo Inc. threatened violence on Monday, while Astumbo Middle School went through a drug sweep Tuesday morning but no contraband was found, the Guam Department of Education said. Education Superintendent Jon Fernandez said any threat of violence is taken seriously, even though the Sodexo employee is no longer at the elementary school. "We are taking all measures to ensure the safety of our students,” Fernandez said in a statement. The department said it will continue working with Sodexo and the Guam Police Department for further updates. Information will also be provided to parents directly from the school. The incident was reported to police late Monday afternoon by Sodexo Resident District manager Mike Schnitger, who referred media questions to the department. READ MORE: No GPD nod, no school drug sweeps Drug sweep at middle school Astumbo Middle School, meanwhile, went through a canine sweep at 9 a.m. Tuesday but no contraband was found, GDOE and Guam Customs and Quarantine Agency public information center Jessi Santos-Torres said separately. GDOE said the school year's first joint canine drug sweep between GDOE and the Guam Customs and Quarantine Agency included four canine or K9 teams and eight school attendance officers. Christopher Anderson, GDOE student support and safety administrator, said Astumbo Middle School was singled out for the operation due to a tip from Guam Crime Stoppers indicating possible drug activity at the Dededo campus. GDOE said the joint operation lasted just over an hour and resulted in 10 positive hits, but no contraband was found. "Our goal is to be proactive in assuring our stakeholders that our campuses are drug-free,” Anderson said in a statement. "Our plan is to continue these sweeps throughout the school year and at campuses across the island." The joint sweeps began last school year in an effort to deter drug activity on campuses and to promote a drug-free workplace throughout GDOE. posts.author: Jacques
posts.text:
Bravo... pour plusieurs raisons :
- l'ambiance de la nuit éclairée par certainement une ville lointaine est parfaitement rendue, les noirs sont profonds et on voit bien le reflet des étoiles
- la composition est (presque) le cas d'école d'un des seuls exemples de l'horizon au centre d'une image lorsqu'on veut accentuer l'idée de miroir
- tu ne t'es pas fait piégé par une sur-exposition si tu étais en mode semi-auto
- la profondeur de champ donne une netteté sur l'ensemble de l'image grâce à un diaphragme suffisamment fermé
- la pose est suffisamment longue mais pas trop pour éviter le déplacement des étoiles dans le ciel ou plutôt la rotation de la terre (je dirais 20sec f/5,6 1600Iso ?)

En terme de format, le vertical 1,5 me semble un peu trop haut pour moi.
Il est maintenant impossible de prendre une photo de ciel de jour comme de nuit sans qu'il y ait un avion en vol. Ici, il y en a 3 qui deviennent un sujet important de l'image puisque le regard retourne sur les pointillés. Après, cela peut être aussi une volonté délibérée, sinon l'effacement serait recommandé.

Enfin, tu n'as pas appliqué la procédure postée dans un commentaire en dessous pour supprimer cette pu... de pub Avast, et là tu as droit à un gage : refaire une autre belle image comme ça ;-)

By Maria Russell 

Most of the moneylenders in the area will purchase products in case you want to sell or loan some money. Therefore, if you are having money problems, do not worry since your problems can be sorted out within the shortest time possible. Below are eight tips on identifying the best pawn shops houston can provide to guide you.

Explore print media options. Most newspapers in the area have a segment where pawnbrokers advertise the services they offer. For this reason, spare sometime and go through a number of dailies and you will be sorted. Furthermore, you will get to see the terms and conditions require of you to engage them.

Asking around is not bad. The area has many friendly people and you can easily locate a shylock through approaching the natives. As a result, take a walk in town, talk to various people and you will get useful leads. In addition, you may talk to your friends, family members, workmates, and neighbors to help you identify a perfect service provider.

Pick a shylock with good rates. You ought to have known by now that shylocks are resellers and not collector of items. In addition, just because you bought your item expensively does not mean that you will get the same rate. As a result, visit various service providers and negotiate the deals before picking one who offers the best.

A reliable pawnbroker must be registered. Never enter into a trap of picking a loan service provider without confirming if he is registered or not. Moreover, with the increase in cases of cons pretending to be pawnbrokers, you do not want to be part of the statistics. Thus, go online and confirm with the search engine if your prospective expert is licensed.

Decide whether you want to sell or acquire a loan. Pawnbrokers usually have an option to either give a loan or buy the product from a client. As a result, you need to know the options that are available, consequences of each of them and decide on one. The choice you pick should revolve around your ability to pay the loan on time and value you place on the item.

Do your part of the homework. It is not advisable to put your trust in humans since they are likely to lead you astray. Therefore, whether you got the referrals from someone you trust or not, you should exercise caution at all the times. Moreover, everything a pawnbroker tells you should not be taken as the gospel truth.

Be ready to prove your claims. Whenever you take your property to a pawnbroker, then you should be able to substantiate your claims in order to close the deal. For instance, if it is a jewelry, then you should get an appraisal from an expert who will prove how much the item costs. Consequently, you will not have a problem convincing shylock.

Honor your part of the deal. You need to remember that the deal you make with a pawnbroker is not a gentleman agreement and if you do not honor your part, then you will attract a lot of penalties. In addition, you may even be forced to forfeit your property that meant a lot to you. Hence, ensure that you pay all your bills on time and get your valuable back.

posts.text:
Hallo Zusammen,
ich habe das Phänomen das ich nun langsam in einer Sauna lebe.
Seit der Umschaltung von kühlen auf heizen sind die Regler irgendwie am durchdrehen.
Meine Konfiguration: Der Regler ist schaltende PI-Reglung (PWM) und die Heizungsregler sind auf schaltend 1 bit eingestellt.
Wenn ich die Werte abfrage kommt dabei heraus SOLL Wert 19° und wenn ich IST abfrage oder auf den Thermometer schaue 25°.
Dann schaue ich ab und an auf mein Heizkreis im Stockwerk und sehe das die Ventile auf sind und noch mehr Wärme befördert wird.
Sehe ich ebenso im Gruppenmonitor.
Ich hab nun schon den Betriebsmodus auf Economy umgeschalten und überall ist soll von 17°. Aber weiterhin werden die Aktoren angesprochen?!?
Komisch ist das es im ganzen Haus so ist, also nicht nur ein Regler sondern alle. Letztes Jahr war das nicht so.
Kann mir jemand helfen, ich habe keine Ahnung was da gerade schief läuft, das ging eigentlich immer, auch im Sommer ging das kühlen ohne Probleme.
Vielen Dank
Carsten

posts.title: Netanyahu confidant questioned in corruption probe
posts.text: First Published: 2017-11-07 Netanyahu confidant questioned in corruption probe Israeli PMs diplomatic envoy, relative Molcho identified as one of two men questioned over suspected graft in purchase of German submarines. Middle East Online , Germany signed a deal to sell three Dolphin submarines from ThyssenKrupp to the Israeli navy JERUSALEM - Israeli Prime Minister Benjamin Netanyahu's diplomatic envoy was identified Tuesday as one of two men questioned this week in a probe into suspected corruption around the purchase of German submarines. Yitzhak Molcho was on Sunday and Monday questioned by police along with David Shimron, a relative of Netanyahu and his family lawyer who also represented German industrial giant ThyssenKrupp in Israel. Authorities released their identities on Tuesday. Molcho, a lawyer who partners with Shimron and is also a relative of the Netanyahus, announced last month that he would step down from his position as Netanyahu's envoy in February next year. While his position had no formal title, Molcho led peace negotiating teams with the Palestinians and served as the Israeli premier's pointman for resolving sensitive issues with Egypt and Jordan. Police refused to divulge why Molcho was questioned, saying merely it was part of the submarine affair, but media said he was suspected of having used his position to advance the deal. Last month, Germany signed a deal to sell three Dolphin submarines from ThyssenKrupp to the Israeli navy. Negotiations on the sale had been frozen for three months due to concern in Berlin over the corruption investigation in Israel. The investigation involves officials from the Israeli security establishment as well as those working locally for ThyssenKrupp. Shimron has already been detained for questioning over the affair. Netanyahu himself has not been named as a suspect in the submarine case. He is however being investigated in two separate graft probes and is expected to be interrogated again in the coming days. The two other probes involving Netanyahu centre on the premier allegedly receiving luxury gifts from wealthy supporters and suspicions he sought a secret deal for favourable coverage with the publisher of top-selling daily Yediot Aharonot.

Care is delivered by a multidisciplinary approach that includes surgeons, speech and swallowing therapists, respiratory therapists, physical and occupational therapists, social workers, discharge planners, dieticians and nurses.

On this unit there is an emphasis on patient and family teaching to ensure a level of comfort and confidence for self care when they are discharged to home.

posts.title: Пилот Audi Рене Раст завоевал титул чемпиона DTM 2017
posts.text:
07.11.2017 / АЦ Волгоградский / Новости автосалонов / Москва 
АЦ Волгоградский гордится каждой победой Audi. 
Тридцатилетний заводской пилот Audi Рене Раст (René Rast) завоевал титул чемпиона DTM 2017 года, вписав свое имя в историю мирового автоспорта. Немецкий гонщик одержал победу в своем дебютном сезоне в DTM, ранее подобного результата удалось достичь только итальянскому гонщику Николе Ларини (Nicola Larini) 24 года назад. В первый день финального уик-энда DTM в Хоккенхайме, Audi также удалось завоевать чемпионские титулы в зачете производителей и команд. 
Рене Раст стал седьмым в истории участником знаменитой гоночной серии кузовных автомобилей, который смог завоевать этот престижный титул в первый же сезон выступлений. До 2017 года пилот из Миндена (Minden) лишь трижды принимал участие в отдельных гонках DTM. 
Сезон 2017 года, ставший для Рене Раста дебютным в DTM, оказался по-настоящему впечатляющим. Уже на первом этапе в Хоккенхайме Раст впервые завоевал право начать гонку с первой линии стартовой решетки. Через две недели, на трассе Лаузицринг (Lausitzring), он впервые в своей недолгой карьере в DTM сумел подняться на призовой подиум, а в третий гоночный уик-энд сезона, в Будапеште одержал первую победу. Благодаря ей — также впервые — Раст смог выйти в лидеры серии, и этот статус позднее переходил несколько раз из рук в руки между немецким пилотом и Маттиасом Экстрёмом. В Москве и на трассе Red Bull Ring в Шпильберге (Spielberg) Раст добился еще двух побед в гонках. Помимо этого, он трижды стартовал с поул-позиции и в общей сложности четыре раза показывал лучшее время круга в гонке. 
С 2011 года Раст выступает под флагом бренда с четырьмя кольцами. За рулем спорткара Audi R8 LMS GT3 он, в первую очередь, зарекомендовал себя как пилот, с которым успех гарантирован. Его победы в 24-часовых гонках в Дейтоне (Daytona), Спа (Spa) и на трассе Нюрбургринг (Nürburgring) являются великолепным подтверждением такой репутации, так же как и завоеванные им чемпионские титулы сначала в серии ADAC GT Masters, а теперь и в чемпионате DTM. Рене Раст родился 26 октября 1986 года в Миндене. Сейчас немецкий пилот живет в Брегенце (Bregenz), на австрийском берегу озера Констанц, со своей подругой Дианой и сыном Лиамом (Liam), который родился незадолго до рождества 2016 года. В повседневной жизни — кстати, как и Маттиас Экстрём — он использует в качестве «корпоративного» автомобиля Audi SQ7. 
Следите вместе с нами за победами Audi. 
Мы ждем вас в АЦ Волгоградский на Волгоградском проспекте, 41/1.

Mitsubishi Motors Turns To Profit In H1 On Higher Volume; Reaffirms FY Outlook November 07, 2017, 02:45:  Japanese automaker Mitsubishi Motors Corp. (MMTOF.PK, 7211) reported Tuesday that its first-half net income attributable to owners of the Parent was 48.4 billion Japanese yen, compared to a net loss of 219.6 billion yen in the prior-year period. 
Operating profit was 44.2 billion yen, compared to operating loss of 31.6 billion yen last year. Operating margin improved to 4.7% from prior year's negative margin of 3.7 percent. 
Revenues for the first half rose 9.6% to 947.7 billion yen from 864.9 billion yen a year ago. 
Increased sales in these markets offset slower growth in North America, where sales rose 1% to 72,000 units, and a 1% decline in unit sales to 89,000 units in Europe. 
Further, the company reaffirmed its full-year outlook for the current fiscal year. 
Looking ahead, for fiscal 2017, the company continues to expect attributable net income of 68 billion yen, and operating profits of 70 billion yen, representing a 3.5% operating margin. 
Net sales are still projected to rise 5% year-on-year to 2 trillion yen. 
The company continues to forecast that global sales would increase by 11% year-on-year to 1.029 million units.

thread.title: Début de soirée
thread.title_full: Début de soirée

posts.author: Jacques
posts.text:
Bravo... pour plusieurs raisons :
- l'ambiance de la nuit éclairée par certainement une ville lointaine est parfaitement rendue, les noirs sont profonds et on voit bien le reflet des étoiles
- la composition est (presque) le cas d'école d'un des seuls exemples de l'horizon au centre d'une image lorsqu'on veut accentuer l'idée de miroir
- tu ne t'es pas fait piégé par une sur-exposition si tu étais en mode semi-auto
- la profondeur de champ donne une netteté sur l'ensemble de l'image grâce à un diaphragme suffisamment fermé
- la pose est suffisamment longue mais pas trop pour éviter le déplacement des étoiles dans le ciel ou plutôt la rotation de la terre (je dirais 20sec f/5,6 1600Iso ?)

En terme de format, le vertical 1,5 me semble un peu trop haut pour moi.
Il est maintenant impossible de prendre une photo de ciel de jour comme de nuit sans qu'il y ait un avion en vol. Ici, il y en a 3 qui deviennent un sujet important de l'image puisque le regard retourne sur les pointillés. Après, cela peut être aussi une volonté délibérée, sinon l'effacement serait recommandé.

Enfin, tu n'as pas appliqué la procédure postée dans un commentaire en dessous pour supprimer cette pu... de pub Avast, et là tu as droit à un gage : refaire une autre belle image comme ça ;-)

우리는 그리스도와의 교제를 더욱더 가져야 한다 .
그는 자기 제자들을 동산으로 인도하여
거기서 자신이 사랑하므로 고통받으심에 대하여 증
인이 되게 하신다 .
그리스도의 교회는 울타리 쳐진 동산 ,
즉 그가 몸소 가꾼 그의 동산이다 .
그리스도를 만나고자 하는 사람들은
그의 동산 , 즉 교회에서 그와 만날 것을 기대해도 좋다 .
그들은 그가 정하신 규례 안에서 ,
또한 그의 말씀과 성례식 ,
그리고 그가 항상 ,
즉 세상 끝날까지 우리와 같이 하실 기도를 통하여
그를 섬겨야 한다 .
그리스도가 그의 교회에 오실 때에는
그의 양무리를 먹이시기 위함이다 .
그는 다른 목자들과 같이 울타리 없는
평원에서 먹이시는 것이 아니고
그의 동산에서 먹이신다 .
그는 그의 친구들을 먹이기 위하여 오시며
또 그들로 인하여 기뻐하신다 .
왜냐하면 여호와께서는
그를 경외하는 사람들을 기뻐하시기 때문이다 .
그는 많은 동산을 갖고 계시다 .
즉 각기 다른 크기와 형태를 가진 많은 교회가 있다 .
그러나 그들이 일단 그의 것이면
그는 그들 중에 자신을 명백히 나타내시며
그들로 인하여 크게 기뻐하신다 .
그는 백합화들을 하나 하나 따서는
그 앞에 다 모으신다 .
그리고 마지막 날에 한꺼번에 추수하실 것이다 .
그리고 사랑하는 자에게 불친절하게 대했으며
그는 당연히 그녀에게서 떠나갔다 .
그러므로 성도들이 실수하거나
그리스도께서 눈살을 찌푸리시는 경우에라도
그리스도와 성도간에 항상 굳게 유지되어
온 언약을 새로이 할 만한 경우가 발생한 것이다 (<시 89:30- 35>).
" 나는 내 임무에 부주의하고 게을렀나이다 ."
우리는 그리스도의 사랑에 대해
확신할 수 없을 때라도 믿음으로 그를 따라야만 한다 .
" 내가 전에 받곤 했던 위로를 지금 느끼지는 못하지만
나는 계속해서 그리스도는 내게 속하였고
나도 그에게 속하였다는 사실을 믿고 의지하리이다 ."
- 메튜헨리 아가서 주석 (18) -

BERLIN (AP) — German automaker BMW AG says its third-quarter earnings were 1.8 percent lower than a year earlier as a result of increased costs for investments, research and development. 
The luxury car maker said Tuesday that it earned 1.79 billion euros ($2.08 billion) in the July-September period, down from 1.82 billion euros last year. Revenue edged up 0.3 percent to 23.42 billion euros from 23.36 billion euros. 
The company said the BMW Group, which also includes Mini and Rolls-Royce, delivered 590,415 vehicles in the third quarter, 1.2 percent more than a year earlier. Its core brand was helped by the new 5 Series, launched in February. 
BMW said it is forecasting a “solid” increase in pre-tax profit for the full year, having previously predicted a “slight” rise. Most Read Stories

French Jewish author wins France's top literary prize French Jewish author Olivier Guez won the Renaudot award, one of France's top literary prizes, for his book "The Disappearance of Josef Mengele". The journalist who writes for various French and international publications spent years retracing the secret post-Holocaust life of the SS doctor, notorious as the "Angel of Death" at the Auschwitz concentration camp for his often lethal experiments on prisoners. Date: Nov 06, 2017, 05:04 PM
 Social: Author Olivier Guez: "I wanted to know what Mengele's life was like afterwards, whether he had been punished or not. I think in Europe today (with the rise of the far-right) we need to understand the extraordinary mediocrity of evil.''
PARIS--- French Jewish author Olivier Guez won the Renaudot award, one of France's top literary prizes, for his book "The Disappearance of Josef Mengele".
The journalist who writes for various French and international publications spent years retracing the secret post-Holocaust life of the SS doctor, notorious as the "Angel of Death" at the Auschwitz concentration camp for his often lethal experiments on prisoners.
Mengele managed to escape to Argentina and even got a West German passport in his own name in the 1950s so he could return for a holiday in his hometown.
"I wanted to understand what is left of a person after they have done that kind of evil," Guez, 43, said after winning the prize.
"I wanted to know what Mengele's life was like afterwards, whether he had been punished or not. I think in Europe today (with the rise of the far-right) we need to understand the extraordinary mediocrity of evil," he added.
One of Guez previous books, "The impossible return, a history of Jews in Germany since 1945,’’ won the Prize of best book of Jewish history and research in 2007.
Another book about the Nazis by French Eric Vuillard won this year's top Prix Goncourt. ‘’L’Ordre du Jour’’ (in English The Agenda) recounts the story of how German industry and finance backed Adolf Hitler.

posts.title: Samsung Ad Mocks The iPhone And Apple Fanboys
posts.text:
Akshay Bhalla Nov 7, 2017 
I love my Apple phones just as much I love Samsung's mobile devices but a new advertisement from the South Korean giant has me left rolling on the floor. Samsung tends to poke fun at Apple and their fanboys on a regular basis but this time they actually took it a step further and left everyone in splits. 
The ad is called 'Grow up with an upgrade to Galaxy' and the video shows all the past iPhone launches and mocks the different features that were lacking or were changed over the years. For example, the iPhone 3GS was mocked for its lack of storage space while the iPhone 5s had no support for a stylus. Samsung also pointed out that their smartphones have been waterproof long before Apple jumped on the bandwagon. Apple added water-resistance to the iPhone 7 just last year and Samsung had to point out that they were the first to achieve that, way back in the day. © YouTube 
Towards the end, Samsung poked fun at the iPhone 7 for not having the headphone jack and lack of support for wireless charging. Apple added Qi-wireless charging to the iPhone 8/8 Plus and X which is long after Samsung added the wireless charging feature to their range of smartphones. © YouTube 
By the end of the video, the iPhone fanboy had switched to a Samsung Galaxy Note 8 while walking past a bunch of iPhone fanboys, standing in line for the iPhone X - including a man rocking a haircut that looked eerily similar to the iPhone X notch. Conveniently leaves out exploding Samsung Note 🤷🏼‍♂️ https://t.co/RMhCrF5SpW — Zac Hall (@apollozac) November 6, 2017 
We can't forget that Samsung has had their own share of downfalls such as the exploding Note 7, which was entirely skipped in the video. Samsung likes to take a dig at the iPhone whenever they get the opportunity to do so and just last month, the Korean smartphone giant released an ad for the Galaxy S8 that celebrated the OLED display a day before the iPhone X pre-orders were set to go live. We don't want to spoil the entire video for you so we suggest you check it out below and laugh along with us. Don't Miss

posts.text:
University of Michigan Admin Specialist Assoc Health in Ann Arbor , Michigan 
How to Apply 
A cover letter is required for consideration for this position and should be attached as the first page of your resume. The cover letter should address your specific interest in the position and outline skills and experience that directly relate to this position. 
Job Summary 
Background: 
The mission of Michigan Medicine is to create the future of healthcare through the discovery of new knowledge for the benefit of patients and society; educate the next generation of physicians, nurses, health professionals and scientists; and serve the health needs of our citizens. Michigan Medicine refers to the university´s academic medical center which includes all of the patient care, education and research areas, and ranks as one of the top academic health centers in the country. 
This position is a member of the Office of the Executive Director (OED), University Hospital and Frankel Cardiovascular Center (UH/CVC). The person in this role will support the administrative activities of the UH/CVC Associate Chief Clinical Officer (ACCO), as well as work together with the OED administrative team to provide overall support to the administrative and operational functions of the UH/CVC OED. 
The successful candidate in this role will be responsible for supporting the administrative work of the UH/CVC ACCO and the OED executive-level leadership team by working together with the OED administrative support team to ensure the overall successful administrative function of the UH/CVC Office of the Executive Director. It is expected that this role will have a strong customer service focus, and that she/he will represent the UH/CVC ACCO and the OED in a professional manner, requiring the confidence, competence and discretion to interact on a daily basis with UMHS leadership, departmental customers, and administrative professional peers. This position involves a high degree of flexibility, requiring the ability to work proactively, both independently and as part of a team, with initiative and creativity. The person in this role is joining a team whose foundation is based upon the UMHS Values of Caring, Teamwork, Innovation, and Trust, and will be expected to adopt and follow these values as he/she executes the responsibilities of this role. 
Responsibilities* 
Support the administrative responsibilities of the UH/CVC ACCO and the OED through the execution of administrative and operational activities of the office which include , but are not limited to: 
Perform advanced, diversified, and confidential administrative duties in support of the administrative responsibilities of the UH/CVC ACCO, along with the UH/CVC OED, and executive leadership team, requiring broad and comprehensive experience, outstanding interpersonal skills and independent judgment based upon experience. 
Manage correspondence and communication (verbal, written, and e-mail) using independent judgment, and requiring a high degree of confidentiality, discretion, and professionalism. 
Provide complex calendar management, exercising discretion and judgment to analyze and appropriately prioritize complicated and challenging calendars 
Provide high-level, pro-active support for executive and other key meetings, including scheduling, meeting material and agenda content tracking and preparation, attending meetings and taking minutes and/or notes, tracking action items and decisions made, and generating all necessary follow-up correspondence to ensure work is completed as appropriate to support related meeting business, projects and/or phases of associated projects, and to prep for subsequent meetings 
Develop, execute and manage a plan for coordinating UH/CVC OED directed events, retreats, and site visits as needed, including timeline development, action items, budget planning and reconciliation, logistics, agenda planning and catering 
Responsible for defined parts of small projects or phases of larger projects in support of the OED and/or UH/CVC segment initiatives 
Resolve routine and complex inquiries from inception to resolution, including those regarding highly confidential matters and urgent/emergent operations issues, in a timely and efficient manner 
Screens/triaging telephone calls and visitors 
Provide administrative coverage for Executive Director, Chief Nursing Officer, and Associate Hospital Directors as required 
Coordinates all aspects of business travel itineraries and arrangements as business necessitates 
Provide and coordinate information and materials for upcoming presentations and/or analysis 
Assists with designing, editing, and reviewing presentation materials for content, grammatical, and/or presentation style correction, ensuring that deadlines are met and all materials required are correct and assembled 
Accesses, understands, and appropriately utilizes UM proprietary database/software systems (M-Pathways, Finance BI (Oracle), Concur, PDS3, MReports, etc.) 
Reconcile P-Cards and other expense reports 
Represent the department by attending and participating in unit events and/or serving as OED representative/liaison in institutional programs across the clinical enterprise 
Other responsibilities and/or projects as assigned 
Required Qualifications* 
Associate or Bachelor’s degree or an equivalent combination of education and experience with at least four to five years of executive-level administrative office experience supporting executive leaders and initiatives including those with large scope, timelines, and budgets 
Demonstrated ability to work independently, showing sound judgment based upon experience, as well as the capability to work as part of a diverse team in a professional and collaborative manner 
Ability to analyze, compare, and evaluate various courses of action, and make independent decisions on matters of significance free from immediate direction. 
Experience with project coordination and support 
Must be able to analyze, manage and appropriately prioritize scheduling for extremely busy high-level calendars 
Ability to assess competing priorities, manage workflow, and meet operational deadlines. 
The skill to handle confidential materials and situations with professionalism, sensitivity and discretion is required. 
Exceptional customer service skills and professional demeanor 
Excellent written and verbal communication skills with a high degree of interpersonal skills 
Exemplary attention to detail with strong proof reading and grammar skills 
Demonstrated strong Microsoft Office (Outlook, Word, PowerPoint, Excel) skills 
Familiarity with a broad range of UM proprietary applications such as Concur, Finance BI, M-Pathways 
Demonstrated knowledge and experience within the University of Michigan Health System 
Must be flexible, resourceful, and work well under pressure 
Desired Qualifications*
